# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
# Types: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, test, chore
# Scope: service name or module (optional)
# Subject: imperative mood, no period at end
# Example: feat(metrics): add CPU usage monitoring
#
# Body (optional): More detailed description
#
# Footer (optional):
# BREAKING CHANGE: description
# Closes #123, #456
#
# Rules:
# - Type is required and must be lowercase
# - Subject line should be 72 chars or less
# - Use imperative mood in subject line
# - No period at end of subject line
# - Separate subject from body with blank line
# - Use body to explain what and why (not how)
# - Can use multiple lines with "-" for bullet points
